text: Matiari is a city in Sindh, Pakistan. Matiari may also refer to: *Matiari District, an administrative unit of Sindh, Pakistan *Matiari Taluka, a tehsil of Matiari District. *Matiari, Nadia, a census town in Nadia district, West Bengal, India ==See also== * * Matiaria, a village in Bihar, India * Mateare, a municipality in Nicaragua
title: Matiari (disambiguation)
